<section class="container mb-5">
    <p>
        EXID is a five-member girl group group that debuted on August 13, 2012 under AB Entertainment which later became Banana Entertainment.
        The original six-member lineup debuted in February 2012, but three of those members left soon afterwards and were replaced by two others.
        Today they are under different companies and are focusing on their solo careers.
        Because there is no single company to update about EXID's activities, LEGGO News aggregates their updates from all of the sources to one place.
    </p>
</section>


