        <div id="solji" class="tab-pane active">
            <div class="card">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="video-column col-4">
                        <video class="img-fluid rounded-start" controls>
                            <source src="~/home/solji.mp4">
                        </video>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-8">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title">솔지 (Solji)</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">
                                Full name: 허솔지 (Heo Solji)<br>
                                Born: January 10, 1989<br>
                                Profession: Singer, Professor
                            </p>
                            <p class="card-text">
                                Solji debuted as a singer on March 31, 2006 in the duo 2NB.
                                The duo never saw success even after many releases, so Solji left 2NB in 2012 to be a vocal coach instead.
                                She was the vocal coach for EXID before she became a member.
                            </p>
                            <p class="card-text">
                                When three of the original members of EXID left soon after their debut, Solji was asked to join along with Hyelin to replace them.
                                Solji's debut as a member of EXID was August 13, 2012.
                            </p>
                            <p class="card-text">
                                Today Solji is a highly respected vocalist in Korea and is one of the best singers.
                                She is a professor in the Department of Applied Music at Yongin University.
                                She still sings and releases music too.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div id="elly" class="tab-pane">
            <div class="card">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="video-column col-4">
                        <video class="img-fluid rounded-start" controls>
                            <source src="~/home/elly.mp4">
                        </video>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-8">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title">엘리 (ELLY)</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">
                                Full name: 안효진 (Ahn Hyojin)<br>
                                Born: December 10, 1990<br>
                                Profession: Rapper, Songwriter, Producer
                            </p>
                            <p class="card-text">
                                ELLY debuted as a rapper on September 12, 2009 at the HIPHOPLAYA concert as a member of the underground rap group Jiggy Fellaz.
                                In 2011, she got into songwriting and quickly had success with the award-winning song "Trouble Maker".
                            </p>
                            <p class="card-text">
                                It was revealed in December 2011 that the talented ELLY would be a member of the upcoming kpop group EXID.
                                She debuted as one of the original members on February 14, 2012.
                            </p>
                            <p class="card-text">
                                ELLY is one of the most credited female songwriters in Korea, writing most of EXID's songs and many songs for other groups.
                                Today ELLY works at TR Entertainment as a producer for TRI.BE.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div id="hani" class="tab-pane">
            <div class="card">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="video-column col-4">
                        <video class="img-fluid rounded-start" controls>
                            <source src="~/home/hani.mp4">
                        </video>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-8">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title">하니 (Hani)</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">
                                Full name: 안희연 (Ahn Heeyeon)<br>
                                Born: May 1, 1992<br>
                                Profession: Singer, Actress
                            </p>
                            <p class="card-text">
                                Hani is an original member of EXID, debuting on February 14, 2012.
                                Hani saved the group from disbandment in 2014 when her fancam went viral and brought EXID a lot of positive attention.
                                Her fancam is still the most viewed fancam of all time.
                            </p>
                            <p class="card-text">
                                Recently Hani has been focusing on acting and psychology.
                                As an actress, she has been successful and has experimented in a variety of roles.
                                As a psychology expert and celebrity, she uses many platforms to help others achieve better mental health and well-being.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div id="hyelin" class="tab-pane">
            <div class="card">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="video-column col-4">
                        <video class="img-fluid rounded-start" controls>
                            <source src="~/home/hyelin.mp4">
                        </video>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-8">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title">혜린 (Hyelin)</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">
                                Full name: 서혜린 (Seo Hyelin)<br>
                                Born: August 23, 1993<br>
                                Profession: Singer
                            </p>
                            <p class="card-text">
                                Hyelin debuted as a member of EXID on August 13, 2012.
                                She along with Solji replaced the three members who had left the group earlier that year.
                            </p>
                            <p class="card-text">
                                Hyelin is an expert on food, beauty, sales, and laughter.
                                She sometimes appears on shows related to food, beauty, or sales; 
                                and her personality transforms even the most mundane topic into quality entertainment.
                            </p>
                            <p class="card-text">
                                Hyelin is also a great singer.
                                When Solji went on haitus, Hyelin sang her parts during performances.
                            </p>
                            <p class="card-text">
                                While Hyelin's activities recently are mostly her various appearances and endorsements, she does release some music too.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div id="jeonghwa" class="tab-pane">
            <div class="card">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="video-column col-4">
                        <video class="img-fluid rounded-start" controls>
                            <source src="~/home/jeonghwa.mp4">
                        </video>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-8">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title">정화 (Jeonghwa)</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">
                                Full name: 박정화 (Park Jeonghwa)<br>
                                Born: May 8, 1995<br>
                                Profession: Singer, Actress
                            </p>
                            <p class="card-text">
                                Despite being the youngest member of EXID, Jeonghwa has been in the entertainment industry the longest.
                                Jeonghwa started her career as an actress in December 2004 after being scouted at a talent show a few months prior.
                                She was in several shows and even a music video when she was a kid.
                            </p>
                            <p class="card-text">
                                On February 14, 2012 Jeonghwa debuted as a member of EXID.
                            </p>
                            <p class="card-text">
                                Jeonghwa's focus recently is on her acting career.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
